name: 2DN
description:
An illustration-focused model. Works for both SFW and NSFW generations. Test this model and others for free on Discord.

You may also be interested in my MapleSyrup model.

Update (5 Feb 23):

DiffusionBee users should use the Pruned PickleTensor version as it has the VAE baked in, which is needed for the vibrant colours.
